Leng Ji!

00:30:03.550 --> 00:30:04.200
Yingtao,

00:30:04.480 --> 00:30:06.790
hindi ka masyadong uminom at nakatulog,

00:30:06.790 --> 00:30:08.920
hinahayaan mo siyang umalis
